title: Worlds Missions Bug

embed.description: The easy way to save screenshots, GIFs, and websites. Make everyone happy by sharing smarter, faster, and with your point crystal clear.

body: I completed all the Worlds missions but it says that i have only 3/4 completed.

replies.body: There were a few issues with some of these missions not correctly completing, but as of right now your account looks like it's at the right place with the progress of that mission. You should be getting more missions as Worlds progresses, so no worries about not having that one finished yet.
